    <constraint source="ADR-029">Publish hygiene — verify `dotnet publish` ≤60 MB compressed. No new NuGet packages.</constraint>
    <constraint source="project">CLAUDE.md §10 Placement Justification REQUIRED in PR notes (per CLAUDE.md §10 binding workflow rule).</constraint>
    <constraint source="project">CVE check (NFR-09): `dotnet list package --vulnerable --include-transitive` returns 0 new HIGH-severity findings.</constraint>
    <constraint source="project">Field shape: `DateTimeOffset` on the C# DTO (matches Dataverse `modifiedon` semantics — UTC-anchored with offset). Serialized as ISO-8601 string on the wire; frontend TS type is `string` (formatted with Intl.DateTimeFormat or Fluent UI date helper at render time).</constraint>
    <constraint source="project">Manage pane render: format the date consumer-side using locale-aware formatting; do NOT pre-format on the server. Server emits ISO-8601 raw.</constraint>
    <constraint source="project">JSON casing: camelCase on the wire (`modifiedOn`), per existing endpoint convention. Confirm by reading `ChatEndpoints.cs:36` JsonOptions or the equivalent in workspace endpoints.</constraint>
  </constraints>

